[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/overcalls"]
[Student "S"]
{NORTH has a normal overcall of 1\S.

SOUTH has a really good hand, but he doesn't have to worry about missing a slam since NORTH will 
not have more than 16 points. So he just bids what he thinks NORTH can make, 4\S.}

