[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/overcalls"]
[Student "S"]
{WEST has 12 points and a good enough suit to overcall 1\H.

EAST has 9 points with a good \D stopper. She bids 1NT.

WEST has nothing more to say, and lets EAST play 1NT.}

